@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fwezlm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.48 / v0 + 0.73) / wp.sin(v2 + 0.02)))
    tmp = wp.sin(v1)
    tmp = (v2 / v2)
    v2 = (v1 * wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.80)))
    v0 = v0
    v0 = 0.25
    data[tid] = v0
